26:15.705 --> 26:16.774
Huh!

27:19.869 --> 27:21.969
<i>Hi, you've reached René.</i>

27:21.971 --> 27:23.471
<i>Leave a message.</i>

27:23.473 --> 27:25.440
Hey.

27:25.442 --> 27:27.077
Hey, it's me.

27:28.479 --> 27:30.649
I haven't called in a while.

27:31.882 --> 27:34.085
At least not since last year.

27:35.452 --> 27:38.420
I'm actually in town
on business.

27:38.422 --> 27:41.422
It's crazy how this town
stays the same.

27:41.424 --> 27:45.059
I saw Pete down on 9th Street
selling Christmas trees.

27:45.061 --> 27:48.932
That guy's got to be, like,
a million years old by now.

27:50.166 --> 27:52.167
What does he sell
in the summertime?

27:52.169 --> 27:53.869
Palm trees?

27:57.907 --> 27:59.843
I know, I know,
it's corny.

28:00.911 --> 28:02.413
But I bet you laughed.

28:06.784 --> 28:08.153
Anyways, um...

28:09.753 --> 28:12.321
just wanted to wish
you a Merry Christmas,

28:12.323 --> 28:14.092
and...

28:16.493 --> 28:18.096
and I miss you.

29:37.307 --> 29:39.510
<i>Quit playing with the lights.</i>

29:42.346 --> 29:44.481
I'm sorry.
It won't happen again.

29:46.983 --> 29:49.220
<i>For your own safety.
I'm not trying to hassle you.</i>

29:50.320 --> 29:52.019
No, no, you're right.

29:52.021 --> 29:53.357
I'll be more careful.

30:31.595 --> 30:32.963
Eww.

30:36.066 --> 30:37.836
God.

30:46.609 --> 30:49.880
Hello? Is...
is someone out there?

30:54.984 --> 30:56.250
Hello?

30:56.252 --> 30:58.388
Is there someone there?

32:30.213 --> 32:31.950
Sure, why not?

32:37.121 --> 32:38.423
Hmm.

32:56.272 --> 32:58.442
All right,
what do we got?

33:10.421 --> 33:12.557
Oh, buddy,
what happened to you?

33:52.261 --> 33:53.530
Now what?

34:10.146 --> 34:11.782
Oh, God, stop!

34:13.282 --> 34:14.551
Stop!

34:34.471 --> 34:36.474
Come on, come on, come on.

34:59.195 --> 35:01.199
Come on, where are you?

35:06.869 --> 35:09.574
What is that?

35:24.253 --> 35:25.655
Wait.

35:32.329 --> 35:33.397
Oh!

35:39.202 --> 35:40.471
Fuck.

36:07.697 --> 36:10.664
I think we have a problem here.

36:16.773 --> 36:19.507
I think... I think
we have a bad connection.

36:19.509 --> 36:21.778
If you can hear me,
the power is out.

36:23.413 --> 36:24.679
<i>Stay where you are.</i>

36:24.681 --> 36:26.583
<i>I'll see if...</i>

36:28.351 --> 36:29.650
Come again?

36:33.289 --> 36:34.458
Hello?

36:39.262 --> 36:40.530
Come on.

37:26.510 --> 37:27.845
Hello?

37:43.427 --> 37:45.492
You know, technically
this is trespassing,

37:45.494 --> 37:47.431
and I will call the police.

38:17.059 --> 38:18.663
Hello?

38:31.541 --> 38:33.611
Hey, I'm talking to you.

38:47.423 --> 38:48.858
Excuse me.

41:49.639 --> 41:51.039
<i>Hello?</i>

41:51.041 --> 41:52.840
<i>Is anyone there?</i>

41:52.842 --> 41:54.979
Yes, I can hear you.

41:55.778 --> 41:57.514
<i>Please help me.</i>

41:59.114 --> 42:02.583
Who is this?
What's happening to you?

42:02.585 --> 42:04.619
<i>There's something...</i>

42:04.621 --> 42:07.956
<i>th-th-there's something
behind my eyes.</i>

42:07.958 --> 42:09.923
Where are you calling from?

42:09.925 --> 42:13.596
<i>Send help to the American
Building, Apartment 1106.</i>

42:15.097 --> 42:17.197
No, no. I'm...

42:17.199 --> 42:19.002
I'm the only person
here tonight.

42:20.836 --> 42:23.771
This building's been vacant
for almost 30 years now.

42:25.842 --> 42:29.309
<i>Oh, God, I can feel it
crawling inside of me.</i>

42:29.311 --> 42:30.878
Just breathe.

42:30.880 --> 42:32.880
<i>I see what it sees.</i>

42:32.882 --> 42:34.882
<i>Make it stop!</i>

42:34.884 --> 42:36.617
<i>Make it stop!</i>

42:36.619 --> 42:38.621
<i>Make it stop!</i>

42:39.789 --> 42:41.054
<i>I'm going to cut it out.</i>

42:41.056 --> 42:43.023
No, no, no, no.
Don't do that.

42:43.025 --> 42:45.959
<i>I don't know how much longer
I can last.</i>

42:45.961 --> 42:49.630
<i>There's something inside of me.</i>

42:49.632 --> 42:51.999
<i>It's...</i>

42:53.802 --> 42:55.403
<i>it's an angel.</i>

42:55.405 --> 42:57.371
<i>It's an...</i>

42:57.373 --> 42:58.875
Hello?

43:04.114 --> 43:06.016
Are you still there?

43:13.356 --> 43:15.292
<i>Wait. Wait.</i>

43:16.092 --> 43:17.791
<i>It stopped.</i>

43:17.793 --> 43:18.959
<i>I think it...</i>

43:41.150 --> 43:42.952
Oh!

44:27.963 --> 44:29.365
No.

44:41.277 --> 44:42.275
No.

44:42.277 --> 44:43.813
No, no, no.

44:55.324 --> 44:56.859
What?

45:29.958 --> 45:31.194
What?

45:34.963 --> 45:36.733
This can't be right.

45:49.978 --> 45:51.748
Plan B.

46:09.264 --> 46:10.900
What?

46:18.340 --> 46:20.243
Come on, come on, come on.

46:21.476 --> 46:23.246
Please.

46:44.032 --> 46:45.967
No.

46:45.969 --> 46:47.436
Oh, God, no.

50:56.385 --> 50:58.422
They don't make them
like this anymore.

52:04.353 --> 52:07.720
To the entity that resides
in this building...

52:07.722 --> 52:09.492
I call to you.

52:39.588 --> 52:41.490
Come on, answer me.

53:03.913 --> 53:06.449
I demand to know
who I'm talking to.

53:24.599 --> 53:26.435
You're not welcome here.

53:47.456 --> 53:48.856
By whom?

54:03.405 --> 54:05.574
What do you want from me?

54:31.500 --> 54:32.965
No! No!

